eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker

Class TypeTrackerBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker.TypeTrackerBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITypeTracker
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbapTypeTracker, CLikeTypeTracker

    public abstract class TypeTrackerBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITypeTracker
    Abstract base class for type trackers.

    While this base class itself does not keep any state and is thread-safe, implementing classes may introduce such behavior.

    See Also:
